OL,3,CThree hikers dead and 20 missing after
OL,4,Cvolcano erupts in Indonesia
OL,6,FVideo captured by Alex Djangu, a local
OL,7,Ftour guide, shows the moment Mount
OL,8,FDukono erupted
OL,10,FAt least three hikers have been
OL,11,Fkilled, and 20 others are missing
OL,12,Fafter a volcano erupted in Indonesia,
OL,13,Flocal officials said.
OL,15,FThe Singaporean nationals were killed
OL,16,Fwhen Mount Dukono, on the island of
OL,17,FHalmahera in North Maluku province,
OL,18,Ferupted Friday morning, a search and
OL,19,Frescue official on the island said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
