OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778284974
OL,3,CThree hikers dead and 20 missing after
OL,4,Cvolcano erupts in Indonesia
OL,6,FA rescue operation to find the others
OL,7,Fis underway.
OL,9,FDramatic footage recorded near the
OL,10,Fcrater by Indonesian mountain guide
OL,11,FAlex Djangu shows a huge column of
OL,12,Fsmoke and ash rising above the
OL,13,Fmountain.
OL,15,FDjangu was guiding two German tourists
OL,16,Fon Mount Dukono when he felt deep
OL,17,Ftremors before the eruption.
OL,19,FHe told ITV News' North American
OL,20,Fpartner CNN it was "very scary".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
