PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778284974
OL,3,CThree hikers dead and 20 missing after
OL,4,Cvolcano erupts in Indonesia
OL,6,F"I saw the small rocks and gravel
OL,7,Fsliding down because of the tremors,
OL,8,Fthen I told my clients we have to run
OL,9,Fdown," he said.
OL,11,FDjangu and his group managed to get to
OL,12,Fsafety, but he said many other hikers
OL,13,Fremained at the crater when the
OL,14,Fvolcano erupted.
