OL,3,CThree hikers dead and 20 missing after
OL,4,Cvolcano erupts in Indonesia
OL,6,FHe added: "When we were about 100
OL,7,Fmetres away, I saw two groups of local
OL,8,Ftourists, one group of nine people
OL,9,Falready close to the rim and the other
OL,10,Fwere videoing for content."
OL,12,FPhotos from Indonesia's national
OL,13,Fsearch and rescue agency BASARNAS show
OL,14,Frescue teams on the mountain, carrying
OL,15,Fat least one injured person on a
OL,16,Fstretcher through the forest.
