OL,3,CThree hikers dead and 20 missing after
OL,4,Cvolcano erupts in Indonesia
OL,6,FIndonesia sits on the "Ring of Fire",
OL,7,Fa band of seismic activity that
OL,8,Fcircles the Pacific Ocean, stretching
OL,9,Ffrom Japan and Indonesia to California
OL,10,Fand South America, making it one of
OL,11,Fthe most earthquake and volcano-prone
OL,12,Fregions on the planet.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
